episodes.title: Exploring the secret world of Plymouth Brethren Christian Church
episodes.description: All week and in an upcoming documentary, CityNews is looking at a exclusive Christian Sect. The Plymouth Brethren Christian Church. So what is this religion and where did it start? Pat Taney reports.

episodes.title: Leaving the Jehovah's Witnesses
episodes.description: A rare and revealing look inside the Jehovah's Witnesses from three people who have left the religion
